Class InternshipApplication

java.lang.Object
team5.InternshipApplication
public class InternshipApplication extends Object
Represents a student's application to an internship opportunity. This class tracks the relationship between a student and an internship, including the application date and current status. Application statuses progress from PENDING to SUCCESSFUL/UNSUCCESSFUL, and finally to ACCEPTED when a student confirms their placement.

      applicationID - the unique identifier for this application
      internship - the internship being applied to
